chunk_content: PT Participation: Defined as enrollment or participation in at least one round of a local, national, regional, and/or international external quality assurance or proficiency testing program within the reporting period. Specimen received for testing: A specimen is received for testing if its arrival at the POCT site was recorded in a register/logbook and/or LIS within the reporting timeframe.
